name: Hi, I'm Mitchell
body:
### Mitchell Tilbrook
I'm Mobile and Web developer in Syndey, Australia. I'm currently the lead Android developer at SeatFrog a travel start-up here in Sydney. When I'm at work and developing a side project I like to have fun riding the motorbike, push-bike, or uni-cycle, walking thought the national parks around my house. When possible getting tougher  with friends to have a game of Dungeon and Dragons.

### Projects
I've become obsessed with working on [RxJava for Android by kaushik](https://github.com/kaushikgopal/RxJava-Android-Samples) I've even ported it to [Kotlin](https://github.com/marukami/RxKotlin-Android-Samples) also working on getting a set of [Rx .NET](https://github.com/marukami/Reactive-Xamarin-Samples). 


### Development
I also love learning new programing language right now I'm chewing on F#, Elixir, Kotlin. 


### Support or Contact
Twitter: [@sir_tilbrook](https://twitter.com/sir_tilbrook)

Github: [marukami](https://github.com/marukami/)
